statement:
select b.city
,c.division_en as divison
,f.department as department_id
,f.category as category_id
,concat(f.department,'-',c.department_en,'-',c.department_cn) as department
,concat(f.category,'-',c.category_en,'-',c.category_cn) as category
,a.upc
,f.upc_desc
,count(distinct a.order_id) as order_nums
,count(distinct a.delivery_phone) as user_nums
,count(distinct case when d.delivery_phone is not null then a.delivery_phone end) as pi_sensitive_user_nums
,max(e.all_order_nums) as all_order_nums
,count(distinct a.order_id)/max(e.all_order_nums) as order_penetration
,count(distinct a.order_id)/count(distinct a.delivery_phone) as purchase_frequency
,count(distinct case when d.delivery_phone is not null then a.delivery_phone end)/count(distinct a.delivery_phone) as pi_sensitive_customer_rate
from (
     SELECT *
     FROM bi_secure.order_line as a
     where paid_date<='2021-11-28'
     AND paid_date>='2020-12-01'
     AND channel='SNG'
     and store_id not in (5050,5500,5598,104,5712,34031,34071)
     and delivery_phone is not null
     ) as a
left join (
          select delivery_phone
          ,lowpi_order_rate
          from bi_secure.promotion_analyst_user
          where order_nums>=3
          and lowpi_order_rate>=0.5
          ) as d on a.delivery_phone=d.delivery_phone
left join bi_secure.store_info as b on a.store_id=b.store_id
left join (
          SELECT b.city
          ,count(distinct order_id) as all_order_nums
        FROM bi_secure.order_line as a
          left join bi_secure.store_info as b on a.store_id=b.store_id
          where a.paid_date<='2021-11-28'
          AND a.paid_date>='2020-12-01'
          AND a.channel='SNG'
          and a.store_id not in (5050,5500,5598,104,5712,34031,34071)
          and a.delivery_phone is not null
          group by b.city
          ) as e on b.city=e.city
left join bi_secure.daily_update as f on a.upc=f.upc
left join bi_secure.new_categroy_1 as c on f.department = c.department_no and f.category = c.category_no
where c.department_no in (2,4,8,13,26,40,46,90,91,1,82,92,96)
and f.upc_desc not like '%降解袋%'
and f.upc_desc not like '%塑料袋%'
and f.upc_desc not like '%购物袋%'
group by b.city
,c.division_en
,f.department
,f.category
,concat(f.department,'-',c.department_en,'-',c.department_cn)
,concat(f.category,'-',c.category_en,'-',c.category_cn)
,a.upc
,f.upc_desc

table_meta.bi_secure.store_info:
CREATE TABLE `store_info` (
  `store_id` int(11) NULL COMMENT "",

  `store_name` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `store_type` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `region` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",

  `province_en` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `city` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `city_en` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `dm` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `address_cn` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `longitude` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `latitude` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `go_date` date NULL COMMENT "",
  `sng_open_date` date NULL COMMENT "",
  `jddj_open_date` date NULL COMMENT "",
  `wmdj_open_date` date NULL COMMENT "",
  `is_jddj_store` varchar(200) NULL COMMENT "",
  `is_wmdj_store` varchar(200) NULL COMMENT "",
  `is_sng_store` varchar(200) NULL COMMENT "",
  `is_wfs_store` varchar(200) NULL COMMENT "",
  `store_status` int(11) NULL COMMENT ""
) ENGINE=OLAP 
DUPLICATE KEY(`store_id`)
COMMENT "from cn_ec_bi_dl_secure.store_info"
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`store_id`) BUCKETS 1 
PROPERTIES (
"replication_num" = "1",
"in_memory" = "false",
"storage_format" = "DEFAULT"
);
